title: Westpac now sees no New Zealand rate cut in Nov
text:
Westpac now sees no New Zealand rate cut in Nov

Stock Markets 1 hour ago (Oct 31, 2019 09:21)

© Reuters. Westpac now sees no New Zealand rate cut in Nov SYDNEY, Oct 31 (Reuters) - Westpac economists have changed their call on New Zealand interest rates and now expect no cut at the Reserve Bank of New Zealand's (RBNZ) policy meeting on Nov. 13. The shift from the influential house, saw the dollar extend an overnight rally to reach $0.6408 NZD=D3 and move away from Wednesday's low of $0.6335.
